The '''Whiphid healing trance''' was a special ability exhibited by certain [[Whiphid/Legends|Whiphid]], most notably the [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[K'Kruhk]]. A Whiphid using this trance would lower their metabolism to the point where they sometimes seemed to be [[Death/Legends|dead]], but in fact, their body would be repairing its injuries. During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], K'Kruhk used this ability several times to survive what would otherwise have been fatal wounds.

